# RailsHx Client Library Configuration
#
# Browser builds use this library for typed RailsHx/Hotwire client helpers
# without loading the Ruby target compiler or Ruby-only Haxe std overrides.
# The shared `std/` surface intentionally contains both browser-safe RailsHx
# client APIs and shared typed tokens such as Turbo stream names/targets.

-cp ${SCOPE_DIR}/std/

-D railshx.client=0.0.0
